    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>快节奏的第一人称机甲射击动作游戏</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1584280/extras/4b81f56105f6e39462b0554ddeaab6f0.poster.avif?t=1640819323\" width=590 height=184 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1584280/extras/4b81f56105f6e39462b0554ddeaab6f0.webm?t=1640819323\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>Steel Salvo 是一款快节奏的动作游戏。你的机甲装备了用于冲刺和浮悬的器械，两把巨大的枪支和一把充满能量的剑。你面对的每一个机器敌人各有不同，从蜘蛛式的炮塔到蜂拥而至的无人机等......你将要全力以赴并且保持警惕去避免被分解成破铜烂铁！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>富有挑战性的困难模式</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1584280/extras/48c83aec6a6466fecb30a9688b8a4a76.poster.avif?t=1640819323\" width=590 height=184 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1584280/extras/48c83aec6a6466fecb30a9688b8a4a76.webm?t=1640819323\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>战胜普通模式去解锁更具有挑战性的困难模式吧！倍增的敌人会给你送去枪淋弹雨。谨记：如果你保持移动的话或许还能侥幸生还！把困难模式称为炮弹地狱也不为过呢！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>多彩的的角色配音</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1584280/extras/e4c4d0debcc0207f99285fc128b5cfc8.poster.avif?t=1640819323\" width=590 height=184 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1584280/extras/e4c4d0debcc0207f99285fc128b5cfc8.webm?t=1640819323\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>在这短暂的故事里，你是海王星最后的希望！跟你的指挥官和机甲机械师会面吧。当然也少不了那卑劣的机器之王！角色们都附有多彩的英文配音并配有多国语言的字幕。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>创作者:</strong></h2>Hugues ANTIPHON - Leo COMPE - Julien DI NATALE 